### 原生 Coze OpenAPI 兼容：工作空间列表（v1）
# @name openSpaceList
GET {{host}}/v1/workspaces?page_num=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@workspaceId = {{openSpaceList.response.body.data.workspaces[0].id}}
@memberUserId = 1

### 原生 Coze OpenAPI 兼容：工作空间列表（api/v1 别名）
GET {{host}}/api/v1/workspaces?page_num=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
